        <span>Open Collective</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Donation</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://newsletter.coollabs.io/"
      target="_blank"
      class="button flex items-center gap-4 w-64 justify-center"
    >
      <svg
        class="w-10 h-10"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        <g
          fill="none"
          stroke="#fff"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path
            d="M3 7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V7z"
          ></path>
          <path d="m3 7l9 6l9-6"></path>
        </g>
      </svg>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span>Newsletter</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Sponsorship</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="pt-4">
    We are a <span class="text-warning font-bold">bootstrapped</span> company. We
    rely on your support to keep the project alive. <br />This helps to focus on
    the actual users
    <span class="text-warning font-bold">(like You)</span>
    and not on investors / revenue. <br /><br />If you use our self-hosted
    version, you can support our work by donating.
  </div>
  <div class=" pt-16 max-w-xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      Who is behind this<span class="text-warning">?</span>
    </div>
    <div class="text-left pt-20">
      Hey, I'm
      <a
        href="https://twitter.com/heyandras"
        class="underline font-bold inline-flex items-center text-warning"
        >Andras Bacsai <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="3"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-3 h-3 -mt-1 ml-1"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M4.5 19.5l15-15m0 0H8.25m11.25 0v11.25"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <br />
    <div class="text-left">
      I'm a Hungary-based software developer who transitioned into an Indie
      hacker in July 2022. I left my job to pursue my dreams of dedicating my
      full time to open-source projects.<br /><br />If my open-source projects
      simplify your work or you appreciate my efforts, <span
        class="text-warning">please consider donating or sponsoring</span
      >.<br />This will ensure the projects remain free, accessible, and
      continue to evolve, allowing me to dedicate my full time to creating and
      improving them. <br /><br />It significantly benefits me in the long term!
      <br /><br />Thank you for your support! <svg
        class="w-4 h-4 inline-block"
        viewBox="0 0 36 36"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        <path fill="#FFDC5D" d="M3 26h8v10H3zm22 0h8v10h-8z"></path>
